The,service,provides,information,about,altitude,and,topography,for,places,on,the,Earth,Sources,for,topographic,data,include,the,Shuttle,Radar,Topography,Mission,SRTM,and,the,GTOPO,project,of,the,U,S,Geological,Service,USGS,Data,describes,contours,and,primary,features,of,all,continents,except,Antarctica,at,a,horizontal,resolution,of,about,meters,API,methods,support,submission,of,a,place,or,list,of,places,specified,by,latitude,and,longitude,or,GPS,coordinates,to,retrieve,altitude,distance,apart,and,intermediate,locations,The,API,generates,an,altitude,profile,for,the,route,between,the,specified,places,which,can,help,to,route,s,steepness,or,to,verify,the,visibility,of,one,point,from,another,Distance,measurements,account,for,the,curvature,of,the,Earth